tip.text: The sticky toffee pudding comes in two possible forms. Custard or ice cream. Unless your taste buds are immune/crippled, the custard is sweetness overkill. Each portion is good for two persons.
The Haddock fish is unexpectedly light (no strong fishy taste). The freshness of the fish is apparent upon the first bite. A good alternative to chips are the mozzarella cheese sticks.
Looking for something British to go with tea? No, not scones but crumpets! And they will have Earl Grey from 15 May '17. Jean Luc Picard would be pleased.
Quick, affordable and quality burger & chips lunch!The regular lunch menu (not the upgrade to 6 oz) comes with a 15 minute guarantee, or the next lunch is on them.
There is only one main on the regular menu and you cannot go wrong with this steak. I recommend the chips and (amazingly buttery) béarnaise sauce to go with. If you love steak, this place is a must!
The Vanilla Cheesecake is a must have for anyone with a sweet tooth. And lactose tolerant, of course.
The lobster roll is amazing. As is the service. It is a fancy establishment, so dress up and enjoy yourself.
Grab a seat first and order your burger at the bar when you've made up your mind. It's going to be good.
The cheeseburger comes on the plate by itself so if you want it instagrammable, share the plate with some fries like I did. The cheese on the fries was not worth it IMO. But the burger was awesome.
Free phone for use during your stay, but if you do use it, remember to erase all data on it with the menu on the top left before you leave. I was able to access past user data that wasn't wiped.
The Mushroom & Mascarpone Toastati Melt has a layer of mushrooms that you don't see until you sink your teeth in them.
The Mac & Cheese is amazing to me, but it may be a little gelatinous for some. Best with a light refreshing drink.

The roast chicken can be a bit dry but very tender. As for the ginseng chicken, the taste is blended to a mild but pleasant taste even for those who hate ginseng like myself. Try both if possible.
For couples, buy a lock and secure your love onto the fence on the second level in the open area. Please do not throw your keys over the fence as you may have heard, it is considered littering.
